&lt;ol&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;
	&lt;ol&gt;
		&lt;li&gt;What is the purpose of the change&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;/ol&gt;
	&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;


&lt;p&gt;    This PR updates the error handling in the webUI to support Flip6. Error reporting was standardized with the REST rework, but is slightly different than in the past.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    The existing error handling code was checking whether the response contained an `error` field (or just returned the entire payload if the status code indicates an error), whereas with the rework every error has contains an `errors` array.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    Various checks were added to account or both cases.&lt;/p&gt;

